cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.SD, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with learning representations from multimodal time series data, which involves machine learning and natural language processing. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also mentions speech recognition and sentiment analysis, which fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) respectively. Finally, the regularization method proposed in the paper involves tensor rank minimization, which is related to cs.SD (Systems and Control).
